 if (hasRecordAudio && state.currentCaptureMethod == AudioCaptureMethod.STANDARD) {
 viewModel.onAction(EchosAction.AudioPermissionGranted)
 }
}
```
- `permissions` will be a map like `{"android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO" to true/false}`.
- Check `permissions[Manifest.permission.RECORD_AUDIO] == true`.

---

**Summary:** 
- Your lambda parameter is not a `Boolean` (isGranted), but a `Map<String, Boolean>`.
- Fix: Check the actual permission grant status in the returned `Map`.

